channel.title: Breezymode [Collab?]
channel.description:
hey guys ive finished up a few new projects recently and im feeling the urge to break out of my current sound and work with another artist on a new project! I love getting the chance to meet new people on here and discover new artists! Ive collabed with a few people before and i would say im pretty solid at builds and drops but im not limited to exclusively working on those parts. Sorry for the long post but if any of you have those tracks that you started and like it but dont know where to go i love working on those :) Hit me up if you are interested!
;TLDR - Down to collab if you have WIPs you're stuck on
